{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, I was a-- a person with-- I was 16 years old, and a third of my life was-- was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and education in our family and-- and among Jews in general was pretty high on the list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I started looking for-- for someplace to learn something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were beginning to receive these care packages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From our family in the United States who left Narewka in the early 1900s when there were still pogroms in-- against Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brothers-- my-- my mother's brother and my mother's sister went to the United States and established their family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they've lived here since the early 1900s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They assumed that we were dead, at first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had heard about what had happened to Narewka people, and they just assumed that we were included.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then a year or so later, we added our names to the-- to a list of groups of organizations that did searches.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we told them that we had relatives in the United States and this is what our name was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they asked us where they lived, and we said, they live in New York.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, who doesn't live in New York?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, they actually found our relatives and told them that there was a possibility that there are some survivors in Europe who are related.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it turned out that it was true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they proceeded to send papers out for us so that we can come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, my sister and my brother David left Czechoslovakia and went to Israel to live.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- I was with my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
